                <div class="col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-sm-12 col-xs-12 nopad project-box properties-rows clearfix">

                    <!-- <h2 class="section_title_drakgray" style="text-align:center;"><strong></strong></h2> -->
                    <div class="aboutbanner">
                        <img src="~/Content/assets/images/cms/tnt_205824.jpg">
                    </div>

                    <p class="newp" style="text-align: justify;">The Allotment of Plots for the purchaser is based on <strong>"First come First serve basis"</strong> and normally on the following general payment schedule as the booking process. Site Visit will be arranged at any time either before payment of booking or after.</p>
                    <p class="newp" style="text-align: justify;"><strong>General Payment Schedule for Pre-Launch of the Project:</strong></p>
                    <p class="newp" style="text-align: justify;">On Booking&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; - Rs. 1, 00,000/-</p>
                    <p class="newp" style="text-align: justify;">Within 15 days &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; - 30% less initial booking amount</p>
                    <p class="newp" style="text-align: justify;">On Registration &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; -&nbsp;Balance amount within a month.</p>
                    <p class="newp" style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Booking Process:</strong></p>
                    <ul>
                        <li style="text-align: justify;">After receiving booking amount, the chart will be prepared on total application received and matched with the availability.</li>
                        <li style="text-align: justify;">House Sites will be allotted on first come first basis for the application received and remaining application will be kept under waiting list.</li>
                        <li style="text-align: justify;">The notice will be sent to eligible applicants to make the 50% of total amount less booking advance within 30 days from booking date.</li>
                        <li style="text-align: justify;">Buyers who are paying the entire amount on booking stage will be allotted plots based on their preference on first come first serve basis.</li>
                        <li style="text-align: justify;">Applicants who are not paid the amount in stipulated time will get cancelled.</li>
                        <li style="text-align: justify;">Registration expenses is to be borne by the applicant.</li>
                        <li style="text-align: justify;">These indicated payment schedule and allotment procedure can also vary for Project to Project depending on the nature of ownership of the project. Hence, these allotment procedure and payment schedule are <strong>subject to reconfirmation</strong> at the time of booking.</li>
                        <li style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Rights of plot allotment is subject to approval by the Trust and the managements decision is final.</strong></li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

